---
title: Marinated Tofu & Veggie Poke Bowl with Toasted Sesame Dressing & Pickled Cucumber
description: We love poke bowls, because they’re so easy to customise with your favourite flavours. This plant-based version uses
Peking-style tofu, Asian greens, carrot and cucumber, with a nutty sesame dressing to tie the whole thing together.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/tofu-poke-bowl-71285d85.jpg
